quran[11{c,v,t}:
41,1,h m
41,2,yeh khuday-e Rehman o Raheem ki taraf se nazil kardah cheez hai
41,3,"aik aisi kitaab jis ki ayaat khoob khol kar bayan ki gayi hain, arabi zabaan ka quran, unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain"
41,4,basharat dainay wala aur dara dainay wala magar inn logon mein se aksar ne is se ro gardani ki aur woh sun kar nahi dete
41,5,"kehte hain"" jis cheez ki taraf to hamein bulaa raha hai is ke liye hamaray dilon par ghilaaf charrhey hue hain, hamaray kaan behray ho gay hain, aur hamaray aur tairay darmain aik hijaab haail ho gaya hai to apna kaam kar, hum apna kaam kiye jayen ge """
41,6,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, mein to aik bashar hon tum jaissa mujhe wahi ke zareya se bataya jata hai ke tumhara khuda to bas aik hi khuda hai, lehaza tum seedhay usi ka rukh ikhtiyar karo aur is se maffi chaho tabahi hai unn mushrikon ke liye"
41,7,jo zkoh nahi dete aur akhirat ke munkir hain
41,8,"rahay woh log jinhon ne maan liya aur naik aamaal kiye, unn ke liye yaqeenan aisa ajar hai jis ka silsila kabhi totnay wala nahi hai"
41,9,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn se kaho, kya tum uss khuda se kufar karte ho aur dosaron ko uss ka humsartehraتے ho jis ne zameen ko do dinon mein bana diya? wohi to saaray Jahan walon ka rab hai"
41,10,uss ne ( zameen ko wujood mein laane ke baad ) oopar se is par pahar jama diye aur is mein barkaten rakh den aur is ke andar sab mangnay walon ke liye har aik ki talab o haajat ke mutabiq theek andazay se khoraak ka samaan muhayya kar diya yeh sab kaam chaar din mein ho gay
41,11,"phir woh aasman ki taraf mutwajjah howa jo uss waqt mehez dhuwan tha uss ne aasman aur zameen se kaha"" wujood mein aa jao, khuwa tum chaho ya nah chaho"" dono ne kaha"" hum aa gay farmabardaron ki terhan """
